{"tid":2490074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk: 今年Level 5","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:38:50.000Z","uid":255650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1456b01382829acf92185729a92b8e4d5dea823d","tid":2490074,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/04/15/teslanorader/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2Fteslanorader%2Flife-tech%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=83eb1882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/04/15/teslanorader/life-tech/</a><br />\n近日 Elon Musk 表示新系統 FSD Beta V9.0 即將面世，只需透過視像鏡頭捕捉影像並移除雷達來達致完全自動駕駛，他相信 Tesla 有望在今年完成 Level 5 的 自動駕駛技術。<br />\n<br />\nElon Musk 在研討會上表示新系統 FSD（Full Self-Driving 全自動輔助駕駛）Beta V9.0 會採用以純視像鏡頭取代雷達來為車輛捕捉視覺資訊的新技術，能在不同的路面狀況和惡劣天氣下有著更好的表現。現時 Tesla 的 FSD 雖然叫「全自動駕駛」功能，但技術只停留在 Level 2 「以駕駛人自駕為主」的階段，離 Level 5 的 「全自動駕駛」仍有一段距離。但隨著 Elon Musk 在世界人工智慧大會的採訪中表示利用攝影鏡頭作偵測的新系統，和提升電腦運算的機制與精密程度後將有望能在今年達到 Level 5 自動駕駛技術的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/WholeMarsBlog/status/1380388899193712642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FWholeMarsBlog%2Fstatus%2F1380388899193712642&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=e80870c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FWholeMarsBlog%2Fstatus%2F1380388899193712642&h=92322d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/WholeMarsBlog/status/1380388899193712642</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmShC3fEWqXVFWBBgQ7EVAeVwjNM8Mef5dvPR6aA6aPQrY?filename=kCcfQdi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCcfQdi.jpg&h=e94c99b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友則質疑新系統面世後是否代表 Tesla 以後不會再為車輛安裝雷達感應器？而 Elon Musk 的回應亦簡短快捷：Remove。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdWySM1Uf8dTjoqJtGBbT6neHsxRqXy4ANCLVU3DeQUo8?filename=Dq73Y6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq73Y6L.png&h=a07550c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，基於現時各國在道路規則和駕駛文化上仍未完全統一，加上因爲半自動駕駛輔助技術所導致的意外也漸多，對於事故後的法律和保險細節仍未有共識，外界猜測就算 Elon Musk 能在短時間内達成自動駕駛的願景，這項技術的普及化也非一朝一夕的事。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源: CARSTUFF"},{"pid":"9b18740c54610d0d4fba66818a6121ff7419d93c","tid":2490074,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"9b4ea610982a11092ad2fcee2216e8d5bc000e9a","tid":2490074,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b18740c54610d0d4fba66818a6121ff7419d93c","tid":2490074,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"哦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ce50ab8b431a35fce8f0715c0bb1db3d7a862c","tid":2490074,"uid":356101,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"吹，繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e6092e6aa0849ad5ab0cb520b7827ca74af59c","tid":2490074,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"散貨味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d8aa87e180fb1455db1e557ae041dbe019571e","tid":2490074,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾老千"},{"pid":"b3f672241d3d04c3d00d3815a46d4c0dbd998b30","tid":2490074,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}